Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.55,0:15:23.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對他們來說也是第一次的體驗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.78,0:15:29.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.94,0:15:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,調整姿勢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.00,0:15:48.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.91,0:15:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃 不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.40,0:16:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔君 血
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.65,0:16:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:04.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.79,0:16:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係 比起內心痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.41,0:16:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體受傷要好的多
