Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.34,0:16:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,諸井那傢伙受傷了 發揮不出力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.92,0:16:26.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒出息 所以說男人什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.60,0:16:27.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.39,0:16:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 四角著地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.36,0:17:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.38,0:17:03.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了啊
