Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.61,0:17:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能暴露了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:42.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.36,0:17:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mix 山茶花
